The Telegraph - Calcutta : Sports

 Special BCCI meeting

Mumbai: The BCCI has convened a special general meeting on May 20. 

On Friday, a proposal to have a three-year term for all BCCI office-bearers without the proviso that they have to be re-elected annually would come up for discussion at the BCCIs constitutional review committee meeting here. (PTI) 




